                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010218-36-defend236 t18010218-36-punish198"></join>
               Whipped in the gaol
            </rs>, and discharged.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Le Blanc.</p>
